data.description: Beautiful and exceptionally well maintained home with 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths. Custom cabinetry and upgraded granite countertops, backsplash, under counter lighting and close assist cabinet doors in kitchen. Bathrooms also have upgraded countertops and close assist cabinet doors. Stainless steel appliances to include gas range and pantry and breakfast nook in kitchen.  Separate dining room. Wired for surround sound in living room and screened in porch. Fiber Optics with port installed in house. Super spacious primary bedroom with brand new carpeting. Primary bathroom boasts double vanity sinks, jetted tub and separate tiled shower with heavy glass doors. Whole house security system, stained front and back screened in porch. Additional concrete grilling pad out back with a gas grill stub out. Garage has a separate side entry door and the floor is completed with an epoxy finish. Attic storage space above garage the size of the garage. The Luxury vinyl plank flooring is really luxurious. Decorative upgraded tile in wet areas and tiled shower. The exterior of home has gutters, soffit lighting, underground sprinkler system and the back yard is completely fenced in. Lawn in lush and landscaped to perfection. Firepit and playset can remain.
